sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Mobile/Admin
    participant Backend
    participant Database
    participant Redis
    
    User->>Mobile/Admin: Enter Credentials
    Mobile/Admin->>Backend: POST /api/auth/login
    Backend->>Database: Verify Credentials
    
    alt Credentials Valid
        Database-->>Backend: User Data
        Backend->>Backend: Generate JWT Token
        Backend->>Redis: Store Session
        Backend-->>Mobile/Admin: Token + User Data
        Mobile/Admin->>Mobile/Admin: Store Token Locally
        Mobile/Admin-->>User: Login Success
    else Credentials Invalid
        Database-->>Backend: No Match
        Backend-->>Mobile/Admin: Error (401)
        Mobile/Admin-->>User: Login Failed
    end
